{"tid":897155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國有團體入稟法院 指政府非法禁止非法入境者申請庇護","createTime":"2018-11-10T16:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T16:08:27.000Z","uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53bce43636db4765e0c12a33fba2afeed8078f40","tid":897155,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"美國有民間團體入稟聯邦法院，指總統特朗普簽署不再庇護非法入境者的公告屬違法，並尋求在訴訟期間，暫緩執行這項命令。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普當地簽署公告，宣布由周六起，拒絕非法入境者的庇護申請，要求尋求庇護的外國人須循正式途徑入境，有效期九十天，不排除會再延長，但已經進入美國境內的移民則不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/trump-issues-decree-limiting-asylum-protection-for-migrants-crossing-illegally-into-the-us/2018/11/09/f856b4ec-e431-11e8-a1c9-6afe99dddd92_story.html?noredirect=on&amp;utm_term=.e67d83591473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fnational-security%2Ftrump-issues-decree-limiting-asylum-protection-for-migrants-crossing-illegally-into-the-us%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2Ff856b4ec-e431-11e8-a1c9-6afe99dddd92_story.html%3Fnoredirect%3Don%26utm_term%3D.e67d83591473&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=2a4ae56d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/trump-issues-decree-limiting-asylum-protection-for-migrants-crossing-illegally-into-the-us/2018/11/09/f856b4ec-e431-11e8-a1c9-6afe99dddd92_story.html?noredirect=on&amp;utm_term=.e67d83591473</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mo6D4YZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMo6D4YZ.png&h=1169f7ef&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}